er);\n      return new SchemaGenerator().makeExecutableSchema(registry, runtimeWiringBuilder.build());\n    }\n  }\n\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777499903378}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_uz4VHhbYUqOe0p5KWAZhSNLp|fc_0f07f7e5996680d00169f27eff2b4881a0bdb4e6769113a3b4", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\nplugins {\n    id \"org.graalvm.internal.tck\"\n}\n\nString libraryVersion = tck.testedLibraryVersion.get()\n\ndependencies {\n    implementation \"com.graphql-java:graphql-java-extended-validation:$libraryVersion\"\n    implementation \"org.jboss.logging:jboss-logging:3.5.0.Final\"\n    implementation \"org.hibernate.validator:hibernate-validator:7.0.4.Final\"\n    testImplementation 'org.assertj:assertj-core:3.22.0'\n}\n\ngraalvmNative {\n\tbinaries {\n\t\ttest {\n\t\t\tbuildArgs.add('--no-fallback')\n\t\t\tbuildArgs.add('-H:IncludeLocales=fr')\n\t\t}\n\t}\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777499903379}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_56cac3PZgVisfbrEHnhy7AJE|fc_0f07f7e5996680d00169f27eff2b5081a0a6f93afae97cbe3e", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "../../source_context/com.graphql-java/graphql-java-extended-validation/19.1-hibernate-validator-6.2.0.Final/main/graphql-java-extended-validation-19.1-hibernate-validator-6.2.0.Final-sources.jar\n../../source_context/com.graphql-java/graphql-java-extended-validation/19.1-hibernate-validator-6.2.0.Final/main/extracted/graphql/validation/locale/LocaleProvider.java\n../../source_context/com.graphql-java/graphql-java-extended-validation/19.1-hibernate-validator-6.2.0.Final/main/extracted/graphql/validation/locale/LocaleUtil.java\n../../source_context/com.graphql-java/graphql-java-extended-validation/19.1-hibernate-validator-6.2.0